System Model Generator Input XML Files

This section lists the various input XML files that are used by System Model Generator to build the system model.

  • Model XML File
  • Shapes XML File
  • Dictionary XML File
  • Localization XML File
  • SystemInfo XML File
  • Dependencies Sysinfo File
  • Legacy Dependencies XML File (for use with 2.0 and earlier System Definitions only)
  • Values XML Files
